query:
SELECT j.id as job_id, j.status as job_status, j.totalImages, j.completedImages, 
       i.id as image_id, i.angleName, i.status as image_status, i.taskId, i.generatedImageUrl, i.errorMessage
FROM multiAngleJobs j 
LEFT JOIN multiAngleImages i ON j.id = i.jobId 
ORDER BY j.id DESC, i.id ASC 
LIMIT 30
